SWAE LEE From The Rap Group RAE SREMURD’S In Love . . . And We Got LINGERIE PICS . . . Of His New GIRLFRIEND!!! February 23, 2017 : Rapper Swae Lee from the group Rae Sremmurd is officially off the market . . . kind of.
You see the rapper is now officially dating an instagram model named Marliesia Ortiz, and we’re told that the two are IN LOVE. 
We said that Swae Lee is only “kind of” off the market, because he’s still accepting applications for any chick looking to be a “side chick”. © 2017 MediaTakeOut
